org.ma.ftc.lib.command

Class MAGamepad

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ma.ftc.lib.command.MAGamepad

  • public class MAGamepad
extends java.lang.Object
    Handles input from standard Joysticks connected to the Driver Station.

    This class handles standard input that comes from the Driver Station by wrapping a Gamepad class. It contains Trigger variables for each input on the gamepad.
